{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"65490af9e9","title":"关于同意争取在旧历年前进攻海南岛的方针的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"df9dd89d25","index":0,"year":1949,"month":12,"day":31,"articleId":"65490af9e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"08910efa46","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，当时任中国人民解放军第四野战军司令员、中南军区司令员。"},{"id":"a1882d4dc6","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓，指邓华，当时任中国人民解放军第十五兵团司令员。赖，指赖传珠，当时任中国人民解放军第十五兵团政治委员。洪，指洪学智，当时任中国人民解放军第十五兵团第一副司令员兼参谋长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2fb227ffbf","type":"title","text":"关于同意争取在旧历年前进攻海南岛的方针的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9"},{"id":"08910efa46","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志（中央转）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9"},{"id":"a1882d4dc6","type":"paragraph","text":"转来邓赖洪廿七日电已悉。同意该电所取方针，即努力争取在旧历年前进攻海南岛，但以充分准备确有把握而后动作为原则，避免仓萃养撞造成过失。为此，邓赖洪应速到雷州半岛前线亲自指挥一切准备工作，并且不要希望空军帮助","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9"},{"id":"4750d99f8f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9"},{"id":"050c6f987b","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月开一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9"}],"page":{"id":"48095a8a86","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65490af9e9","start":110,"end":110}}}},"__N_SSG":true}